@startuml Sequence_UC14
title UC-14: Kelola Pelanggan dan Poin

actor "Admin" as Admin
participant "Halaman Pelanggan\n(livewire/pelanggan)" as View
participant "Customer\\Index\n(Livewire)" as Component
participant "Customer Model" as CustomerModel
participant "PointsHistory Model" as PointModel
database "Database" as DB

Admin -> View: Membuka /pelanggan
View -> Component: mount()
Component -> DB: SELECT customers WITH points_count
DB --> Component: Daftar pelanggan
Component --> View: Render daftar pelanggan

== Cari Pelanggan ==
Admin -> View: Ketik di kolom pencarian
View -> Component: updatedSearch($value)
Component -> CustomerModel: Customer::query()->where('name','like',...)->orWhere('phone','like',...)
CustomerModel -> DB: SELECT customers WHERE ...
DB --> Component: Filtered results
Component --> View: Perbarui tampilan

== Lihat Detail & Riwayat Poin ==
Admin -> View: Klik nama pelanggan
View -> Component: showDetail($phone)
Component -> CustomerModel: Customer::where('phone',$phone)->first()
CustomerModel -> DB: SELECT customers WHERE phone = ?
Component -> PointModel: PointsHistory::where('phone',$phone)->latest()->get()
PointModel -> DB: SELECT points_histories WHERE phone = ?
DB --> Component: Riwayat poin
Component --> View: Tampil modal detail pelanggan

== Tambah Poin Manual ==
Admin -> View: Klik Tambah Poin → isi form → Konfirmasi
View -> Component: addPoints($phone, $points, $note)
Component -> Component: validate(['points'=>'required|integer|min:1'])
alt Validasi gagal
  Component --> View: Pesan kesalahan
else Berhasil
  Component -> PointModel: PointsHistory::create(['phone'=>$phone,'action'=>'manual','points'=>$points])
  PointModel -> DB: INSERT INTO points_histories
  Component --> View: Notifikasi sukses
end

@enduml
